## Graph Scout (every task)

Do **not** load `graphify-out/graph.json` into this chat.

1. **Scout subagent (always)** — at task start, spawn a subagent to query the graph for files/concepts in scope. Return only:
   `{ communities, god_nodes, risk, inbound_callers, recommendation }` — max ~500 tokens.
2. **Drill subagent (if scout reports HIGH/CRITICAL or >1 community)** — inbound edges and blast radius for flagged nodes. Max depth 2.
3. Parent agent plans from the summary only.

Stale graph → `/graphify update .` (AST, no LLM) or full `/graphify .` after large changes.

